      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 82: The original-message parser is invoked from the `text` binding every time the binding reevaluates while `ParsedOriginalBody` is empty. Because parsing is async, hover/layout/model updates can enqueue duplicate parse jobs for the same message, causing unnecessary work and repeated `dataChanged` emissions. Gate the request with an in-flight flag that resets when the parsed role changes or the delegate id changes.\\n```suggestion\\nproperty bool originalParseRequested: false\\nonIdChanged: originalParseRequested \u003d false\\nonParsedOriginalBodyChanged: originalParseRequested \u003d false\\n\\n// ...\\nif (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite) {\\n    if (OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d \\\"\\\" \u0026\u0026 ParsedOriginalBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0) {\\n        if (!originalParseRequested) {\\n            originalParseRequested \u003d true;\\n            MessagesAdapter.parseOriginalMessage(Id, OriginalBody, rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\\n        }\\n        return \\\"\\\";\\n    }\\n    return ParsedOriginalBody;\\n}\\n```",
